original: Frödi, Orvar Emil, advokat, Göteborg, f. 14/9/91 i Gbg. G. 17 m. Westa Cederin. — Stud:ex. v. Gbgs latin 10, hand :inst. 11, jur. kand. 16. Anst. à Nills Olsén Advifcyrå i Gbg sed. 19. Led. av Sv:es advisamf. sed. 21. Hob-bies: segling, tennis o. motorsport.
translated: Frödi, Orvar Emil, lawyer, Gothenburg, b. 14/9/91 in Gothenburg. Married in 1917 to Westa Cederin. - Graduated from Gothenburg Latin School in 1910, Handicraft Institute in 1911, and obtained a degree in law in 1916. Employed at Nills Olsén Law Firm in Gothenburg since 1919. Member of Sweden's advisory council since 1921. Hobbies include sailing, tennis, and motorsport.
